Class ReportCSV

  • java.lang.Object
    • report.Report
      • report.ReportCSV
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LocationReportCSV

    public abstract class ReportCSV
extends Report
    Abstract superclass for all reports using a CSV file. All settings defined in this class can be used for all ReportCSV classes.
